<TEXT id="eP3_圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis" xml:lang="ami" source="ePark3 圖畫故事篇 Southern_Amis" audio="diarized" copyright="CC-BY-NC-SA" citation="Indigenous Languages Research and Development Foundation. (2020). 族語E樂園. https://web.klokah.tw/" BibTeX_citation="@misc{ePark, author = {Indigenous Languages Research and Development Foundation}, title = {族語E樂園}, year = {2020}, url = {https://web.klokah.tw/} }">
    <S id="187147">
        <FORM>Makamelaw i lalan tu cacay a vavuy.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">看見路上有隻豬，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187147.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187147.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187146">
        <FORM>Pahavay ci Kacaw tu cacay a wacu.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">卡照養了一隻狗，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187146.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187146.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187149">
        <FORM>Kalatan nu wacu kira vavuy.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">那隻豬被狗咬傷，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187149.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187149.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187150">
        <FORM>Mamelaw nu i kilangay a nani.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">爬在樹上貓兒看見了，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187150.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187150.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187148">
        <FORM>Kuku’en nu wacu kira vavuy.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">狗追著那隻豬，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187148.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187148.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187153">
        <FORM>Silusid tunu Pangcah ci Panay aci Tipus.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">巴耐和迪布斯穿著傳統服飾，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187153.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15217/187153.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187151">
        <FORM>Tanutawa’ sa kira nani tu vavuy.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">一直笑那隻受傷的豬。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187151.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15216/187151.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187152">
        <FORM>Pilalikidan a davak.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">豐年祭的早上，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187152.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15217/187152.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187156">
        <FORM>Maulah kami a remadiw,a misakeru.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">我們很開心地唱歌跳舞。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187156.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15217/187156.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187155">
        <FORM>Patala tu turun atu sinavel ci ina atu waku.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">媽媽和我準備了糯米糕和很多的菜餚送去，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187155.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15217/187155.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187154">
        <FORM>Vangcal a melawan kuheni.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">她們看起來非常漂亮，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187154.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15217/187154.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187157">
        <FORM>Maratar a lemuwad ku Pangcah tu davak.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">阿美族人清晨早起，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187157.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187157.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187160">
        <FORM>Talalutuk a midungec tu sakalavi’.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">到山上採藤心當晚餐，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187160.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187160.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187161">
        <FORM>I sauwac, i umah, i lutuk ku pingsiyang nu Pangcah.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">溪澗、田間、山中，都是阿美族人的冰箱，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187161.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187161.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187158">
        <FORM>Talasauwac a mivuting tu sakaranam.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">到溪澗捕魚當早餐，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187158.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187158.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187162">
        <FORM>Huvaw! Salipahaksa ku nikaurip nu Pangcah.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">哇!阿美族人的生活多麼快樂。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187162.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187162.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187159">
        <FORM>Talaumah a midateng tu sakalahuk.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">到田間採野菜當午餐，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187159.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15218/187159.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187164">
        <FORM>Hereksa namaranam, malingadtu a dademak.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">吃過早餐，就到田裡工作，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187164.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15219/187164.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187165">
        <FORM>I terung ku cidal, u kalahukantu.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">日正當中，即是午餐時候，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187165.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15219/187165.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187167">
        <FORM>U malalukay a tamdaw ku Pangcah.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">阿美族人是勤奮的民族。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187167.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15219/187167.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187163">
        <FORM>Marekuku’ ku ayam, lemuwadtu ku Pangcah.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">聽到公雞叫，族人就起床，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187163.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15219/187163.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187169">
        <FORM>Adihay ku niyala tu vuting, urang atu kalang.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">捕到許多魚、蝦和蟹，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187169.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15220/187169.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187168">
        <FORM>Talaliyal a mivuting ci yama nu maku.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">我的爸爸出海捕魚去，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187168.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15220/187168.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187170">
        <FORM>Maulah ci ina a makamelaw.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">媽媽看了很開心，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187170.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15220/187170.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187166">
        <FORM>Mucerem ku cidal, u katalumaantu.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">日落西山，準備回家休息，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187166.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15219/187166.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187171">
        <FORM>Tanutawasa ci vaki aci vayi.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">爺爺奶奶笑哈哈，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187171.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15220/187171.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187172">
        <FORM>U kasenengan nu maku ci yama.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">我的爸爸真了不起。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187172.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15220/187172.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187175">
        <FORM>Raraya’ ku cepi’ nu pikawayay.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">綠蝗的大腿長又壯，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187175.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15221/187175.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187173">
        <FORM>Tataang ku mata nu tatakula’.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">青蛙的眼睛大大的，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187173.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15221/187173.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187174">
        <FORM>Vangcal ku sakuvad nu adipapang.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">蝴蝶的翅膀真漂亮，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187174.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15221/187174.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187176">
        <FORM>Maulah ku dadipis a misakeru’.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">蟑螂愉快地在跳舞，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187176.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15221/187176.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187177">
        <FORM>Cicicisa a remadiw ku naninih.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">蟋蟀吱吱地在唱歌。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187177.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15221/187177.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187178">
        <FORM>Ira ku liyal i a’ayaw nu niyaru’ nu maku.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">我的家鄉，前面有大海。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187178.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187178.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187179">
        <FORM>Ira ku lutuk i lalikul nu niyaru’ nu maku.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">我的家鄉，後面有山坡。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187179.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187179.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187180">
        <FORM>Masadak ku cidal, lemuwad ku ayam.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">太陽出現，鳥兒已出巢。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187180.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187180.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187181">
        <FORM>Mucerem ku cidal, taluma’ ku ayam i dipung.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">太陽下山，鳥兒也歸巢。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187181.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187181.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187184">
        <FORM>Misavelavelat ku vuis i kakarayan,</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">天上的星星閃閃發光，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187184.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15223/187184.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187182">
        <FORM>Maherek namicudad tu cacudaden i laviyi’.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">家庭課業在夜裡完成。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187182.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187182.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187187">
        <FORM>Savelevelatsa ku vuis i kakarayan.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">天上的星星閃閃發光，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187187.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15223/187187.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187185">
        <FORM>Ira ku malikatay.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">有的明亮，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187185.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15223/187185.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187186">
        <FORM>Ira ku makahemay.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">有的朦朧，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187186.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15223/187186.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187183">
        <FORM>Pakungku ci ina i tamiyanan a malekaka.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">媽媽給我們姊妹講故事。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187183.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15222/187183.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187188">
        <FORM>Matiya’ u misakemutay nu wawa.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">好像淘氣的小孩。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187188.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15223/187188.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187189">
        <FORM>Masatereptu ku urad.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">雨停了!</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187189.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15224/187189.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187190">
        <FORM>Masadaktu ku talakal ni Adek.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">彩虹出現了!</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187190.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15224/187190.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187191">
        <FORM>Lahngangay, kulawlaway, langdaway.......</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">紅的、黃的、綠的...。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187191.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15224/187191.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187192">
        <FORM>Uwa! Vangcal ku talakal ni Adek.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">哇!彩虹真的好漂亮唷!</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187192.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15224/187192.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187193">
        <FORM>Micael tu aluvu ci vaki aci vayi’.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">爺爺奶奶披掛著肩袋，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187193.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15225/187193.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187194">
        <FORM>Ay! Ay! Ay!</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">唉!唉!唉!</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187194.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15225/187194.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187195">
        <FORM>Vangcal kira aluvu.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">披掛肩袋方便又帥氣，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187195.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15225/187195.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187196">
        <FORM>Pacumud han ni vaki aci vayi ku kamay i aluvu.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">爺爺奶奶手伸肩袋裡，</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187196.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15225/187196.mp3"/>
    </S>
    <S id="187197">
        <FORM>Ira:tu ku icep i kamay nuheni.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh">他們手上就有檳榔。</TRANSL>
        <AUDIO file="圖畫故事篇_Southern_Amis_187197.mp3" url="https://web.klokah.tw/text/sound//15225/187197.mp3"/>
    </S>
</TEXT>
